FBIS4-13811 "drnes079_l_94008" FBIS-NES-94-079 Daily Report 24 Apr 1994 ISRAEL Peres: Rabin Remarks Call For Signal From Syria Peres: Rabin Remarks Call For Signal From Syria TA2404100194 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 0900 GMT 24 Apr 94 TA2404100194 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el Hebrew BFN [Text] Foreign Minister Shim'on Peres said that now, following Prime Minister Rabin's statements on the readiness to evacuate settlements on the Golan Heights in exchange for peace, Syrian President al-Asad had good reason to emit positive signals toward Israel. The foreign minister told our correspondent Hayim Hecht that the change indicated by Rabin's remarks lay in the statement itself and not in its content. The foreign minister added that the government realized that Syria was always slow to react.
